explanation: To complete the task of putting the CD into the safe and moving the DVD from the desk to the safe on the dresser, the objects involved are the CD, Safe, DVD, Desk, and Dresser. The breakdown of execution steps would be as follows: 1. Take the CD and place it inside the safe. 2. Pick up the DVD from the desk. 3. Walk over to the dresser and open the safe. 4. Put the DVD inside the safe on the dresser.
